<p><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span> (4 estrelas): após 3250 minutos estacionado – ganha 90 minutos de bônus;</p>
<p><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span> (5 estrelas): após 5000 minutos estacionado – ganha 120 minutos de bônus;</p>
<p><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span><span class = "glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span> (6 estrelas): após 7000 minutos estacionado – ganha 180 minutos de bônus;</p>
